public ResultPoint[] getResultPoints()
Returns:

getResultMetadata

public java.util.Hashtable getResultMetadata()
Returns:
Hashtable mapping ResultMetadataType keys to values. May be null. This contains optional metadata about what was detected about the barcode, like orientation.
